data.title: Over The Top Moments | Stage 2 | Week 5 | Day 1
London Spitfire Profit and NUS: Access Granted
data.description: Matt “Mr. X” Morello goes to the London Spitfire house to pick up Overwatch League Season 1 champs Profit and NUS for a day of riding paddleboats in the Echo Park Lake. Learn what it’s like finding the proper balance between gaming and going out in this episode of Access Granted presented by Toyota.

data.title: A Very Zen Interview with Jjonak
data.description: Overwatch League Insider Danny Lim sat down with the 2018 MVP Jjonak to discuss his meteoric rise through the Overwatch scene, the highs and lows of last season and where the NYXL go from here.

data.title: Talent Talks That Trash
data.description: The Talent Takedown is finally here and the trash talk is already flying! As our broadcast talent takes the Overwatch stage, find out who is going to back up their words with skill!

data.title: All-Stars Cooking Challenge
data.description: See what the pros can dish up as the Washington Justice, the Houston Outlaws and Atlanta Reign all compete for the title of Overwatch League Cooking All-Stars.

data.title: My Hero: Baptiste
data.description: In this episode of My Hero, learn how the utility-packed support Baptiste impacted the meta from Fusion's EQO, Paris Eternal's Kruise, Excelsior's JJoNak, and San Francisco Shock's Rascal.  It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Learn more at https://overwatchleague.com/en-us/intel-insights!

data.title: Shanghai Dragons Break Through to Their First Stage Playoffs
data.description: It’s no secret that the Shanghai Dragons struggled to find momentum during the Inaugural Season of the Overwatch League. With star DPS players DDing and Diem now leading the charge, Shanghai talks about qualifying for the Stage 2 playoffs and the road ahead.

data.title: The Moms of the Overwatch League
data.description: We invited 5 moms of Overwatch League pros to the Blizzard Arena to hear what their sons had to say about the love and support they’ve received throughout their esports careers. Find out what it means to be one of the #OWLMoms.

data.title: Bumper – A Day in the Life of a Titan
data.description: Sangbeom “Bumper” Park has found himself the vocal and emotional leader of the flawless Vancouver Titans. Follow Bumper as he prepares for a match day and discusses his innate ability to lead his team to victory day in and day out.

data.title: Best of Stage 2 - Overwatch League 2019 Season
data.description: Take a trip from Blizzard Arena to the first Homestand Weekend in Dallas and back again as we review the best moments of Stage 2 in the Overwatch League.

data.title: Meta Report: Stage 2
data.description: In Stage 2, the triple-tank triple-support "GOATS" meta has expanded! In this episode of the Meta Report, learn how heroes like Winston, Ana, Sombra, and Baptiste have made their way into 3-3 comps! It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Learn more at http://www.Intel.com/OWL

data.title: Game/Set with San Francisco Shock’s sinatraa
Laser Battle with Vancouver Titans and Toronto Defiant
data.description: Can the Vancouver Titans extend their win streak even in laser tag? The Toronto Defiant attempt to take them down on and off the keyboard and mouse.

data.title: San Francisco Shock – Now and Then
data.description: The San Francisco Shock knew they had to change things up after placing 9th in the Inaugural Season of the Overwatch League. Super and Moth describe all of the changes that would turn the Shock into a playoff contender in 2019.

data.title: A Perfect Stage for the San Francisco Shock?
data.description: The San Francisco Shock have the opportunity to go a perfect stage, not dropping a single map in 24 maps played. Sinatraa and Rascal sound off on their success and Sinatraa reveals his “dirty secret” that may lead to their victories.

data.title: Dallas Fuel – Fired Up from Homestand Weekend
data.description: After the rowdy Texas crowd nearly tore the roof of the venue, the Dallas Fuel talk about what it was like to finally play in front of a home crowd.

data.title: Atlanta’s Reign over New York
data.description: Do you believe in miracles? Dogman and BabyBay walk through the moments when they managed to take down the juggernauts of the New York Excelsior.
